      "schema:name": "Imagetic Disappropriation",
      "schema:alternateName": [
        "Desapropriação Imagética",
        "Image Disappropriation",
        "Disappropriation of the image",
        "Imagetic disappropriation"
      ],
      "schema:description": "Artistic and epistemological concept formulated by Alexandre Mury within the A.M.O. ontology. Imagetic Disappropriation names the operation by which an image is displaced from its symbolic context of origin and acquires autonomous signification without being reducible to reproduction, parody, homage, pastiche, negation, or conventional appropriation.",
